#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/painting/vertex_paint/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/painting/vertex_paint/introduction.rst:6
msgid "Vertex Painting is a simple way of painting color onto an object, by directly manipulating the color of vertices, rather than textures, and is fairly straightforward."
msgstr "顶点绘制是一种简单通过直接操作顶点的颜色的方法,, 而不是使用纹理来将颜色绘制到物体上, 并且顶点绘制是相当直接的。"

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/painting/vertex_paint/introduction.rst:10
msgid "When a vertex is painted, the color of the vertex is modified according to the rules of the 'brush'. The color of all visible planes and edges attached to the vertex are then modified with a gradient to the color of the other connected vertices. (Note that the color of non-visible faces is not modified)."
msgstr "在绘制顶点时, 将根据 \"笔刷\" 的规则修改顶点的颜色。 然后, 将所有可见平面和边颜色附加到顶点用渐变修改到其他连接顶点的颜色。（请注意，不可见面的颜色不会被修改）。"

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/painting/vertex_paint/introduction.rst:15
msgid "Vertex colors can be painted by first going into Edit Mode, then switching to *Vertex Paint Mode*; however, it will not show up in the render unless you check *Vertex Color Paint* in the :doc:`Materials Options </render/blender_render/materials/properties/options>` panel."
msgstr "首先进入编辑模式，然后切换到 *顶点绘制模式*，就可以绘制顶点颜色。然而，它不会显示在渲染中，除非你勾选 :doc:`材质选项 </render/blender_render/materials/properties/options>` 面板的 *顶点颜色绘制* 选项。"

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/painting/vertex_paint/introduction.rst:23
msgid "Vertex Painting Mode."
msgstr "顶点绘制模式。"

